  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Post traumatic amputees with an experience of over 3 months of prosthesis use at home,
      without any known difficulty using the prosthesis and without stump pathology, using no
      assistive devices, will be examined in a 3 D computerized gait laboratory. Kinematic and
      kinetic parameters of gait will be obtained.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
